<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Py1nmQ20zlMTHGKfNvM++wB4B4tLRGDTnYv4fW3e8D5nv5LKNGAr5ZvI5wUh8tfn" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- Иконки -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!--  Шрифты  -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Code+Pro:ital,wght@1,200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <title>Личный кабинет</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #02341d;
        }

        .card {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card-header {
            background-color: #ff6d00;
            color: #cccaca;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
            position: relative;
            left: 1px;
            top: 20px;
        }

        .card-body {
            border: 2px solid #ffffff;
            height: 430px;
            background-color: #034828;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        h4 {
            text-indent: 10px;

        }

        .avatar {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border: 2px solid #ff6d00;
            border-radius: 19%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
            top: 10px;
        }

        .info {
            font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
            top: 5px;
        }

        .info i {
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .logout1 {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #0057ff;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 9px;
            box-shadow: 30px 12px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
            top: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .logout3 {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #0056fd;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 9px;
            box-shadow: 30px 12px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            left: 110px;
            top: -5px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .logout2 {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #ff6d00;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 9px;
            box-shadow: 30px 12px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
            top: 10px;
        }
        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        h4 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-user-circle me-2" ></i>Добро пожаловать в личный кабинет!</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <img class="avatar" src="{{ user.getAvatar() }}" alt="Аватар">
                    <p class="info"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2" style="color: #ff6d00;"></i>{{ user.getFirstName() }} {{ user.getLastName() }}</p>
                    <p class="info"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2" style="color: #ff6d00;" ></i>Ваши права определены как: {{ user.getRole().getCode() }}</p>
                    <p class="info"><i class="fas fa-envelope me-2" style="color: #ff6d00;"></i>Почта: {{ user.email }}</p>
                    <p class="info"><i class="fas fa-phone me-2" style="color: #ff6d00;"></i>Номер телефона: {{ user.phone }}</p>
                    <p class="info"><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2" style="color: #ff6d00;"></i>Информация о вас: {{ user.info }}</p>
                    <div class="button-group">
                    <div>
                    <a href="http://localhost/send-message" class="logout1">
                        <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt me-2" style="color: #fff;"></i>
                        Чат
                    </a>
                    </div>
                        <div class="button-group">
                            <div>
                                <a href="http://localhost/friends" class="logout3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-friends" style="color: #fff;"></i>
                                    Друзья
                                </a>
                            </div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <a href="http://localhost/login" class="logout2">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt me-2" style="color: #fff;"></i>
                        Выйти из личного кабинета
                    </a>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
